nge/setStart\"><code>setStart()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>setStartBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents\"><code>surroundContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>DOM に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>Range</code></strong> インターフェイスは、ノードやテキストノードの部品を含むことができる文書の断片を表します。</p>\n\n<p>Range は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> オブジェクトの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document/createRange\" title=\"createRange()\"><code>createRange()</code></a> メソッドにより生成することができます。また、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> オブジェクトの <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Selection/getRangeAt\"><code>getRangeAt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> メソッドや <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> オブジェクトの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document/caretRangeFromPoint\" title=\"caretRangeFromPoint()\"><code>caretRangeFromPoint()</code></a> メソッドにより取得することもできます。</p>\n\n<p>さらに、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/Range\"><code>Range()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> コンストラクターも使用できます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>継承しているプロパティはありません。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"range.collapsed\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/collapsed\"><code>Range.collapsed</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>Range の始点と終点が同じ位置にあるか否かを示す <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.commonancestorcontainer\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/commonAncestorContainer\"><code>Range.commonAncestorContainer</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>startContainer</code> と <code>endContainer</code> をともに含む、最も深い <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.endcontainer\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/endContainer\"><code>Range.endContainer</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の終点を含む <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.endoffset\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/endOffset\"><code>Range.endOffset</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>endContainer</code> の中での <code>Range</code> の終点の位置を示す数字を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.startcontainer\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/startContainer\"><code>Range.startContainer</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の始点を含む <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.startoffset\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/startOffset\"><code>Range.startOffset</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd><code>startContainer</code> の中での <code>Range</code> の始点の位置を示す数字を返す</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"コンストラクター","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"range_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/Range\"><code>Range()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>始点および終点がグローバルな <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> である <code>Range</code> オブジェクトを返します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>継承しているメソッドはありません。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"range.setstart\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart\"><code>Range.setStart()</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の始点を設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setend_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEnd\"><code>Range.setEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の終点を設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setstartbefore_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>Range.setStartBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>他の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を基準に <code>Range</code> の始点を設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setstartafter_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>Range.setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>他の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を基準に <code>Range</code> の始点を設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setendbefore_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndBefore\"><code>Range.setEndBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>他の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を基準に <code>Range</code> の終点を設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setendafter_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndAfter\"><code>Range.setEndAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>他の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を基準に <code>Range</code> の終点を設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.selectnode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNode\"><code>Range.selectNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> を、ある <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> とその内容を含むように設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.selectnodecontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNodeContents\"><code>Range.selectNodeContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> を、ある <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> の内容を含むように設定</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.collapse_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/collapse\"><code>Range.collapse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> をその端点の一方へ折りたたむ</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.clonecontents\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneContents\"><code>Range.cloneContents()</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の中身をコピーした <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.deletecontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/deleteContents\"><code>Range.deleteContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の中身を <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> から削除</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.extractcontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/extractContents\"><code>Range.extractContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の中身をドキュメントツリーから <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> に移動</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.insertnode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/insertNode\"><code>Range.insertNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の始点に <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> を挿入</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.surroundcontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents\"><code>Range.surroundContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の中身を新しい <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> の中に移動</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.compareboundarypoints_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareBoundaryPoints\"><code>Range.compareBoundaryPoints()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>2 つの <code>Range</code> の端点の位置を比較</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.clonerange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneRange\"><code>Range.cloneRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>元の <code>Range</code> と同じ端点を持つ <code>Range</code> オブジェクトを返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.detach_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/detach\"><code>Range.detach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>パフォーマンスを改善するために、 <code>Range</code> を使用状態から開放</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.tostring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>Range.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の内容を文字列として返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.comparenode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareNode\"><code>Range.compareNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon obsolete\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n    <title>これは廃止された API であり、動作は保証されていません。</title>\n    <path d=\"M38.75 78.13V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0036.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0033.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0051.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0048.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0066.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0063.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zM36.88 20h26.25l-2.82-6.85a2.35 2.35 0 00-1-.65H40.74a2 2 0 00-1 .65zm54.37 1.88v3.75a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.87 1.87h-5.63v55.55c0 6.44-4.22 12-9.37 12H25.63c-5.16 0-9.38-5.27-9.38-11.72V27.5h-5.62a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.88-1.83v-3.8A1.85 1.85 0 0110.63 20h18.1l4.1-9.78A9.12 9.12 0 0140.63 5h18.75a9.1 9.1 0 017.79 5.22l4.1 9.78h18.11a1.85 1.85 0 011.87 1.87z\"></path>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> が range の前、後、中、外のうちのいずれの場所にあるかを示す定数を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.comparepoint_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/comparePoint\"><code>Range.comparePoint()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>指定された点が <code>Range</code> の前、中、後のうちのいずれの場所にあるかを -1、0、1 で示す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.createcontextualfragment_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/createContextualFragment\"><code>Range.createContextualFragment()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>渡された文字列から生成した <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.getboundingclientrect_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getBoundingClientRect\"><code>Range.getBoundingClientRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> の内容の全体に結びつく <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a> オブジェクトを返します。これは、<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>Range.getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> が返すすべての長方形の集合体です。</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.getclientrects_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>Range.getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd><code>Range</code> 内のすべての要素について、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/getClientRects\"><code>Element.getClientRects()</code></a> の結果をまとめた <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a> オブジェクトのリストを返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.intersectsnode\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/intersectsNode\"><code>Range.intersectsNode()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>指定ノードの範囲が <code>Range</code> と交差するか否かを示す <code>boolean</code> を返す</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.ispointinrange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/isPointInRange\"><code>Range.isPointInRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>与えられた点が <code>Range</code> の中にあるか否かを示す <code>boolean</code> を返す</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-range\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"ja\">Range の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>今後は <code>RangeException</code> は使用せず、代わりに <code>DOMException</code> を使用します。<br>\n    <code>collapse()</code> の第 2 引数を省略可能に変更。<br>\n    <code>isPointInRange()</code>, <code>comparePoint()</code>, <code>intersectsNode()</code> メソッドを追加。<br>\n    <code>Range()</code> コンストラクターを追加。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/DOM-Parsing/#extensions-to-the-range-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Parsing and Serialization<br><small lang=\"ja\">Extensions to Range の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td><code>createContextualFragment()</code> メソッドを追加。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#extensions-to-the-range-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"ja\">Extensions to Range の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td><code>getClientRects()</code> および <code>getBoundingClientRect()</code> メソッドを追加。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Traversal-Range/ranges.html#Level-2-Range-Interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Traversal and Range Specification<br><small lang=\"ja\">Range の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">廃止</span></td>\n   <td>s初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Range","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\" title=\"DOM/DOM_Reference\">DOM インターフェイスの索引</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"コンストラクター","id":"constructor"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Range インターフェイスは、ノードやテキストノードの部品を含むことができる文書の断片を表します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Range","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Range","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"range","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"range","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"range","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"range","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Range","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Range","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Range","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/range","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/range/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Range","title":"Range"}],"pageTitle":"Range - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}